messages.content:
👢 Yee-haw! It’s a wild west build challenge! 🌵 

You’ve traveled the dusty old town road… what do you see? Build something inspired by an old western town! Put on your cowboy hat and get creative! 🤠

:timer: Challenge dates: May 13 - May 25 at 6 PM PDT

__Challenge Guidelines__
:earth: Your creation must be built entirely by you and in Minecraft Earth.
:crafting_table: Your build must be a brand new creation, crafted just for this challenge.
:buildplate: Build your imagination! Challenge theme is open to interpretation and buildplate size won’t be a factor in judging.
:sign: Post your images or video submission and buildplate share link in #wild-west-challenge by the deadline. Feel free to ask a Moderator to pin it!
:challenges: Winning submissions may be used in social media posts.
:fast_parrot: Have fun!
